dback=\"Vrai\"></input> <span>\\\\(5\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HLQZJFWILL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(4\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_HLQZJFWILL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(3\\\\)</span></label><div class='webex-feedback-box'></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"question-buttons\">\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q10-hint', 'Pensez aux propri√©t√©s de l\\'esp√©rance.', 'hint')\">&#10067; Indice</button>\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q10-expl', '\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(2X+1) = 2\\\\mathbb{E}(X) + \\\\mathbb{E}(1) = 2\\\\times 2 + 1 = 5  \\\\)', 'explanation')\">&#128161; Explication</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question-alerts\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q10-hint\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q10-expl\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 11\n\nSoit \\\\(X\\\\) une variable al√©atoire. Si \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X)=0\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X)=1\\\\), quelle est l'esp√©rance et la variance de \\\\(3X+1\\\\) ?\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_VKOHZTJCYD'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VKOHZTJCYD\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(3X + 1) = 3\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(3X + 1) = 1\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VKOHZTJCYD\" value=\"answer\" data-feedback=\"Vrai\"></input> <span>\\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(3X + 1) = 1\\\\) et \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(3X + 1) = 9\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_VKOHZTJCYD\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></inp