babilit√© qu'un √©tudiant r√©ponde correctement √† une question est de \\\\(0.7\\\\). Quelle est la probabilit√© qu'un √©tudiant r√©ponde correctement √† entre \\\\(6\\\\) et \\\\(8\\\\) questions inclusivement ?\n\n<div class='webex-radiogroup' id='radio_DUMMREZFPL'><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_DUMMREZFPL\" value=\"answer\" data-feedback=\"Vrai\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.7004233\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_DUMMREZFPL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.3492134\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_DUMMREZFPL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.6516539\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_DUMMREZFPL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.4740934\\\\)</span></label><label><input type=\"radio\" autocomplete=\"off\" name=\"radio_DUMMREZFPL\" value=\"\" data-feedback=\"Faux\"></input> <span>\\\\(0.1797624\\\\)</span></label><div class='webex-feedback-box'></div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"question-buttons\">\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q14-hint', 'Pour trouver la probabilit√© de r√©pondre correctement √† entre \\\\(6\\\\) et \\\\(8\\\\) questions, il faut additioner \\\\(P(X=8), P(X=7) \\\\text{ et } P(X=6)\\\\).', 'hint')\">&#10067; Indice</button>\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q14-expl', 'Pour calculer la probabilit√© de r√©pondre correctement √† entre \\\\(6\\\\) et \\\\(8\\\\) questions, utilisez la formule de la distribution binomiale : \\\\(P(X = k) = C^k_n p^{k} (1-p)^{n-k} \\\\). On calcule d\\'abord \\\\( P(X=8) = C^{8}_{10} \\\\times  0.7^{8} \\\\times   0.3^{2} =  0.2334744 \\\\), puis on calcule \\\\( P(X=7) = C^{7}_{10} \\\\times  0.7^{7} \\\\times   0.3^{3}  =  0.2668279 \\\\) et on calcule finalement \\\\( P(X=6) = C^{6}_{10} \\\\times  0.7^{6} \\\\times   0.3^{4} =  0.2001209\\\\). La somme de ces trois probabilit√© correspond √† \\\\(0.7004232\\\\).', 'explanation')\">&#128161; Explication</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question-alerts\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q14-hint\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q14-expl\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n## Question 15 (Exercice facultatif üò±)\n\nMontrez que pour une variable al√©atoire \\\\(X\\\\), \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = \\\\mathbb{E} \\\\{(X - \\\\mathbb{E}[X] )^2 \\\\} = \\\\mathbb{E}(X^2) - \\\\{\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\}^2  \\\\).\n\n<div class=\"question-buttons\">\n<button class=\"custom-button hint\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q15-hint', 'D√©veloppez l\\'expression \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = \\\\mathbb{E} \\\\{(X - \\\\mathbb{E}[X] )^2 \\\\} \\\\) et utilisez les propri√©t√©s de l\\'esp√©rance.', 'hint')\">&#10067; Indice</button>\n<button class=\"custom-button explanation\" onclick=\"toggleAlertLegacy('q15-expl', 'On pose \\\\(\\\\text{Var}(X) = \\\\mathbb{E} \\\\{(X - \\\\mathbb{E}[X] )^2 \\\\}\\\\). On d√©veloppe ensuite pour obtenir: \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}\\\\{X^2 + (\\\\mathbb{E}[X])^2 - 2X\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\} \\\\). Par la lin√©arit√© de l\\'esp√©rance, on peut d√©velopper et obtenir: \\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X^2) + \\\\mathbb{E}\\\\{(\\\\mathbb{E}[X])^2\\\\} - \\\\mathbb{E}\\\\{2X\\\\mathbb{E}(X) \\\\}  =   \\\\mathbb{E}(X^2) + \\\\mathbb{E}\\\\{(\\\\mathbb{E}[X])^2\\\\} - 2\\\\mathbb{E}(X) \\\\mathbb{E}(X)     \\\\). Puisque \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\) est une constante par rapport √† l\\'esp√©rance, \\\\(\\\\mathbb{E}\\\\{ (\\\\mathbb{E}[X])^2\\\\} = \\\\{\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\}^2 \\\\), on obtient ainsi: \\\\( \\\\mathbb{E}(X^2) + \\\\{\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\}^2 - 2\\\\mathbb{E}(X) \\\\mathbb{E}(X)  =  \\\\mathbb{E}(X^2) - \\\\{\\\\mathbb{E}(X)\\\\}^2  \\\\)', 'explanation')\">&#128161; Explication</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"question-alerts\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q15-hint\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" id=\"q15-expl\" style=\"display: none;\">\n  <strong class=\"alertType\"></strong>: <span class=\"alertMessage\"></span>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
